channel.title: Need staff that can code on a new Project!
channel.description:
[center]Hey people i am working on a new 317 project and need some staff team. I am not the best for coding but need someone good!
I already purchased a .com domain!
Please message me on skype or reply to this thread if you are down to help!
Skype: Justiino[/center]
